But it does not look well when it is ſo; it makes a man appear contemptible, and a woman a termagant. Come, Mr. Placid, I cannot ſtay another moment. Good night. Heaven bleſs you! 
                           To Lady Eleanor—Good night, my dear Mr. Irwin;


and now, pray take my advice and keep up your ſpirits.
